---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - LastWave">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-white mt-10 mb-6">What is LastWave?</h1>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      LastWave is a web-app that takes data from your last.fm profile and creates a beautiful
      wave graph that represents your music listening trends by artist, album, or tag. The
      artists that you listen to more at a given time has a larger area on the graph.
    </p>

    <div class="w-12 h-px bg-lw-border my-10"></div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Who built LastWave?</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      LastWave is written and maintained by <a href="https://savas.ca/" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">Niko Savas</a>. Swing by my
      <a href="http://last.fm/user/taurheim" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">last.fm</a> profile and say hi!
    </p>

    <div class="w-12 h-px bg-lw-border my-10"></div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Support LastWave</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      Any money donated will go directly to hosting and server costs for LastWave, so that I can keep LastWave
      completely free!
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <a href="http://paypal.me/nikosavas" class="inline-block border border-lw-accent text-lw-accent hover:bg-lw-accent hover:text-lw-bg rounded-lg px-6 py-2 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase transition-all">Donate via PayPal</a>
    </p>

    <div class="w-12 h-px bg-lw-border my-10"></div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Contribute</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      If you're a developer who wants a feature or wants to help develop this tool, please swing by this project's
      <a href="https://github.com/taurheim/LastWave" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">GitHub repository</a> and submit a pull request!
    </p>

    <div class="w-12 h-px bg-lw-border my-10"></div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Technologies</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed mb-12">
      Version 4 of LastWave is built using <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">Astro</a>,
      <a href="https://react.dev/" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">React</a>, and
      <a href="https://www.typescriptlang.org" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">TypeScript</a>. For a full list of dependencies, visit the project's
      <a href="https://github.com/taurheim/LastWave" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-[#00CED1] transition-colors">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
